[Entry, OtherEntry, classifyRow, classifyNested](tuple-field-pattern-lib.ssc)

# Imported tuple-field patterns

```scalascript
println(classifyRow(("customer", "c1", "Ada", "")))
println(classifyRow(("order", "o1", "c1", "10")))
println(classifyRow(("supplier", "s1", "Acme", "")))
println(classifyRow(("customer", 7, "Ada", "")))
println(classifyNested(Some(("ready", Entry("ok")))))
println(classifyNested(Some(("ready", OtherEntry("wrong")))))
```
